name: .COPRESET File Extension
summary: Learn about .COPRESET files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Settings file used by Capture One, a professional photo editing and management application; saves presets that can be applied to multiple photos; can be included in a style (.COSTYLE) with other presets.

content: Capture One presets are often used for adding metadata to images. Common metadata includes the photographer's copyright or branding information.
